# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Agent Instructions (Cross-Agent Consistency)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# AGENTS.md is the single source of truth and MUST be tracked.
# The following 2 files are symlinks created by the setup script (pointing to
# AGENTS.md). They should NOT be committed as separate files — the symlinks
# are recreated on bootstrap, not stored in version control.
